{
  "texts": [
    "For small molecules, a fingerprint was generated for each drug compound using RDKit 119.",
    "For protein/peptide drugs, their weight vectors were calculated along with the protein nodes (see below).",
    "Finally, the SVD method was used to compress each drug vector into a fixed-length vector.",
    "Target nodesTarget nodes were obtained along with the drug nodes, as each drug has one or more specific targets.",
    "The target nodes were weighted according to AD co-morbidities."
  ]
}